message.uploadImageExceed.description: Notification when uploaded image exceeds limit

message.uploadImageError.description: Notification for errors during image upload

message.atLeastOneAdmin.description: Prompt to keep at least one admin

message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: Default inviter's user ID. If the distribution link does not carry the inviter_id parameter, the default user ID is used as the inviter.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: Forced inviter's user ID. If this ID is set, it is used as the inviter regardless of the presence of the inviter_id parameter in the distribution link.

message.originTip.message: Site domain name, bound to site configuration. Cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in the site's meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when the menu bar is expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site admin ID. The user who creates the site initially becomes the admin by default. Only site admins can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: Admins can be added or removed here. Visit https://auth.acedata.cloud for user ID.

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in the site's meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: Keywords can be added or removed here. More precise keywords are better for SEO optimization.
